labels.label:
TIC TAC TOE for NiFi by Dennis Jaheruddin
1. Make sure all processors are stopped and queues are empty 2. Start 'Start Game' and 'Check for Winner' 3. Players can put an X in a box by starting the X processor, or an O by starting the O processor 4. After the winning move the Winner queue starts to fill up (player attribute indicates the winner)
